Description:
In front of you lies a great treasure surrounding a throne on which the remnants of a high naval officer rest. Before you continue, you notice a huge eel carefully watching the skeleton on the throne. A ghostly presence floats beside the eel, contemplating the portrait of a distinguished pirate near the throne.

That must be the legendary Rust King and his trusty pet, Pitt the eel. Together, they were the scourge of the seas long ago!

They stand between you and the obelisk, seemingly unaware of your presence.
DescriptionAction: You may have time to prepare a strategy.
